  <brief_title>Upper Limb Rehabilitation After Stroke Assisted With a Hybrid Electrical Stimulation (ES)-Robot System</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biomechatronic System Using Electromyography (EMG)-Driven Neuromuscular Electrical Stimulation (NMES) for Upper Limb Rehabilitation</official_title>
